==Arabic==
{{phrasebook|ar}}
{{ar-rootbox|ر ح ب}}

===Etymology===
Related to the verb {{m|ar|رَحِبَ|t=to be wide}}. (The verb {{m|ar|رَحَّبَ|t=to make welcome, to receive graciously}} is derived from this term.)

===Pronunciation===
* {{ar-IPA|مَرْحَبًا|مَرْحَبَا|qual2=pausa}}

===Interjection===
{{ar-head|intj|مَرْحَبًا}}

# [[hello]], [[welcome]]

====Descendants====
