* {{desc|ary|مرحبا|tr=marḥba}}
* {{desc|aa|marcabá|bor=1}}
* {{desc|kmr|merheba|bor=1}}
* {{desctree|ota|مرحبا|bor=1}}
** {{desc|tr|merhaba}}
* {{desc|fa-cls|مَرْحَبَا|مَرْحَبًا|bor=1}}
** {{desc|tg|марҳабо|qq=rare, archaic}}
** → Hindustani:
*** {{desc|hi|मरहबा|tr=marhabā}}
*** {{desc|ur|مَرْحَبَا}}
** {{desc|bn|মরহাবা|tr=môrhaba|bor=1}}
** {{desc|ps|مرحبا|tr=marḥabā|bor=1}}
** → Punjabi:
